Entryhall to the Afterlife~
The lighting in this room fights itself.  From below, through a metal
grated floor, red lights and smoke filter eerily upwards.  Many narrow heels
on expensive shoes have been trapped in the narrow holes of the floor. 
Above, though the same style grate, diffuse white light floats downwards. 
The night and fresh air creeps into the Afterlife from the south.  There
appears to be a candle-lit lounge north while stairs up and down sit on
either side of the hallway.  
~
