#5656
Purgatory~
Unlike the grating to the south, this floor is hardwood.  Large rugs have
been laid to support deep backed-velvet couches, better suited in a
Victorian movie.  They are flanked by end and coffee tables made of rich
woods and sporting decorative filigrees.  There are also inviting leather
lounges.  Candles hang in candelabras, they float in decorative bowls, and
rest in etched votive holders.  The music played is soft and rests in the
background.  A straight and sophisticated wooden bar stands here.  The
glasses and bottles behind it are lined up in precise rows.  Instead of a
mirror, patrons look across the bar at paintings of horses and rolling green
countryside.  
~
